{"tid":1328543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄賣港，係鐵一般既事實，請唔好再為其辯護","createTime":"2019-07-18T03:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:35:03.000Z","uid":129792,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d832581a88ed6f6fe61af0eacef46b33612c16a","tid":1328543,"uid":129792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"法律上既問題其他post都講過哂，我唔重覆。<br />\n我想講既係議會入面既問題，有留意開立法會既人都知議會不嬲由建制派玩哂，佢想點屠你就點屠你。而二讀更加係可以任意修改，張超雄條草案上到去比人改99%再通過，你乜都唔會做到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以，我地係一定要反對整個草案</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有，屌你班泛民打手，泛民有錯就要屌架啦。錯就要認，屌就要企定，屌你咪屌你囉而家。分化？分你老母呀，是其是非其非，連咁簡單都唔明，唔怪得你班人會盲目支持泛民班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盲撐同支那愛國撚有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38d290323679d964237c85ff702df25a58c8302","tid":1328543,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=0975de54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n七大訴求<br />\n - 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n - 永久完全撤回逃犯條<br />\n - 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n - 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n - 撤回暴動定性<br />\n - 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n - 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t